cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.CC. 

The paper deals with private information retrieval, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). It also involves the use of databases (cs.DB) and algorithms (cs.DS) to achieve optimal download cost. The concept of achievable rates is related to coding theory (cs.IT) and the exploration of minimum download cost involves optimization (cs.CC).
